cdata.name: AMBT Token
cdata.desc: Ambit Mining is a cryptocurrency mining project that aims to scale its operation to 20 MW and distribute the profits throughout AMBT token holders. The AMBT Token is an Ethereum-based ERC20 Token and holders will be entitled to the profit share from the Ambit mining and hosting operations, which will be paid out bi-weekly in ETH at pro-rata basis.
